 channel magic through their Eidolon, often bypassing traditional arcane methods.\"\n  },\n  Capstone: {\n    MergeWithEidolon: {\n      Mechanics: {\n        Duration: \"Limited\",\n        GainTraits: true,\n        EnhancedCasting: true\n      },\n      Lore: \"The ultimate expression of unity between summoner and Eidolon. A moment of transcendence.\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nSubclasses: {\n  Evolutionist: {\n    Mechanics: {\n      ExtraEvolutionPoints: true,\n      MidCombatMutation: \"Limited uses\"\n    },\n    Lore: \"Focuses on Eidolon as a living weapon, constantly adapting to threats.\"\n  },\n  Conduit: {\n    Mechanics: {\n      EidolonSpellStorage: true,\n      SharedCasting: true\n    },\n    Lore: \"Treats the Eidolon as a magical amplifier and conduit for arcane power.\"\n  },\n  MasterOfMany: {\n    Mechanics: {\n      MultipleSummons: true,\n      EidolonCommander: true\n    },\n    Lore: \"A battlefield tactician who overwhelms enemies with numbers and coordination.\"\n  }\n}\n\nEvolutions: {\n  Examples: [\n    {Name: \"Wings\", Effect: \"Grants flight\"},\n    {Name: \"Breath Weapon\", Effect: \"Area damage\"},\n    {Name: \"Extra Limbs\", Effect: \"Multiple attacks\"},\n    {Name: \"Resistances\", Effect: \"Elemental protection\"},\n    {Name: \"Enhanced Senses\", Effect: \"Darkvision, tremorsense, etc.\"}\n  ],\n  Rules: {\n    PointSystem: \"Spend points to unlock\",\n    Restrictions: \"Some require minimum level\",\n    Respec: \"Allowed during long rest\"\n  }\n}\n\nSpellList: {\n  Cantrips: [\"Mage Hand\", \"Prestidigitation\", \"Thaumaturgy\", \"Minor Illusion\"],\n  Level1: [\"Summon Familiar\", \"Shield\", \"Mage Armor\"],\n  Level2: [\"Misty Step\", \"Mirror Image\"],\n  Level3: [\"Counterspell\", \"Summon Lesser Demons\"],\n  Level4: [\"Dimension Door\", \"Greater Invisibility\"],\n  Level5: [\"Summon Greater Demon\", \"Wall of Force\"],\n  Level6: [\"Planar Ally\", \"Disintegrate\"],\n  Level7: [\"Teleport\", \"Forcecage\"],\n  Level8: [\